description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'KICKSTART YOUR FITNESS JOURNEY! 15-Min Beginner Interval Treadmill Follow Along!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: We have an awesome beginner interval workout for you today! Let's get sweaty!

15 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!
